Package com.paydiant.android.ui.service.deviceinfo

UI services and listener implementations to manage additional device info .

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IDeviceInfoService
    The Interface defining the operations to manage the device specific information, such as device attributes, device specific ids/tokens etc.
    IDeviceInfoServiceListener
    Device Info Manager Service listener to be use with the IDeviceInfoService.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DeviceInfoService
    UI Service implementation of IDeviceInfoService.
    DeviceInfoServiceListenerAdapter
    This class provides an empty implementation for IDeviceInfoServiceListener.
